[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **HTTP Parameter Pollution:**                                                [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ?next=trusted.com&next=attacker.com                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ### JavaScript-Based Redirects                                               [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m When redirect happens via JavaScript:                                        [34m│[0m
