[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ### Host Header Manipulation                                                 [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m Some applications use Host header for redirects:                             [34m│[0m
