[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ### Chaining Open Redirect                                                   [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **Open redirect to OAuth token theft:**                                      [34m│[0m
