[34m│[0m   client_id=X&                                                               [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m   redirect_uri=https://trusted.com/callback?next=https://attacker.com        [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
