[34m│[0m ### HTML Parser Confusion                                                    [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m                                                                              [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m ```html                                                                      [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m Unclosed tags          │ <img src=x onerror=alert(1)                         [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m Self-closing abuse     │ <script/src=x></script/>                            [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m Attribute without =    │ <input onfocus autofocus>                           [34m│[0m
[34m│[0m Backtick in attribute  │ <img src=`x` onerror=alert(1)>                      [34m│[0m
